            <div className="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6 relative z-10">
              <div className="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <Database size={24} />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 className="text-xl font-black text-slate-900">Configuração de Banco de Dados</h3>
                <p className="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Execute este script atualizado no seu SQL Editor do Supabase</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div className="bg-slate-900 rounded-[2rem] p-6 mb-6 relative group">
              <pre className="text-[10px] text-indigo-300 font-mono overflow-x-auto max-h-48 custom-scrollbar">
                {sqlSchema}
              </pre>
              <button 
                onClick={copySql}
                className="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white p-3 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-md transition-all flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest"
              >
                {copied ? <Check size={14} className="text-green-400" /> : <Copy size={14} />}
                {copied ? 'Copiado!' : 'Copiar Script Atualizado'}
              </button>
            </div>

            <div className="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl border border-amber-100">
              <AlertCircle className="text-amber-600 shrink-0 mt-1" size={20} />
              <p className="text-xs text-amber-800 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                <strong>Nota sobre Erro de Cache:</strong> Se você já executou o SQL e o erro "Could not find table" persiste, o Supabase precisa recarregar o cache. Vá no painel do Supabase, em <strong>SQL Editor</strong>, e execute <code>NOTIFY pgrst, 'reload schema';</code> ou reinicie o PostgREST nas configurações de API.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div className="bg-white rounded-[3rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
            <div className="p-8 border-b border-slate-50">
              <div className="relative">
                <Search className="absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400" size={18} />
